    <h1>Bayesian Separation Logic</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-6">Jialu Ho, Nicolas Wu, Azalea Raad · POPL 2026 · <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2507.15530"><img src="/reading/arxiv.webp" alt="arxiv" style="display:inline;height:1em;vertical-align:-0.1em;margin-right:0.2em;"/> arXiv:2507.15530</a></p>

    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">Prereqs: <a href="/reading/natural-breadcrumbs/staton-2025/">🍞 Staton 2025</a> (Hoare triples, wp). Some comfort with probabilistic programming helps.</p>

